        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ESSENTIAL KITCHEN TOOL - The Beille 6-side stainless steel grater is six kitchen tools built into one! Each side of the hexagon-shaped grater offers a different result - fine shred, slice, medium shred, arc slice, course shred and square shred. This space saver is ideal for every kitchen!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "VERSATILE MULTI-FUNCTION GRATER - Grate vegetables like a pro, prepare both soft and hard cheeses effortlessly, extract maximum flavor from citrus with a dedicated zester side, grate breadcrumbs or ginger using finer mesh, or slice cucumbers & other veggies in a breeze using the slicer plane! The Beille 6-in-1 kitchen gadget is a versatile tool that is both handy and indispensable.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Featuring sharp stainless steel blades, this grater will get the job done quickly and result in cleanly sliced and grated food. Its rubber bottom prevents slipping and sliding on your counter, cutting board or plate. The hexagon-shaped grater also prevents food from escaping the bottom of the grater, so you will have less mess to clean up when you're done!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ERGONOMIC AND LIGHTWEIGHT - Designed with comfort in mind the grater has an ergonomic top handle and allows for efficient slicing, grating or shredding. The rubber base provides a firm stand for easy and safe grating. With a lightweight and compact design, it allows the food slicer to take up minimal storage space whether it is displayed on your counter or inside your cabinet.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "CLEAN-UP WITH EASE - Once you are done prepping all your food items, the Beille hexagon stainless steel grater can easily be washed with soap and water or on the top rack of your dishwasher.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "catalog",
            "asin": "B098Z449BH",
            "raw_value": true
        },
