        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Don't limit your grating and slicing potential with just any slicer. The Beille 6-sided stainless steel food grater will quickly become your go-to kitchen tool for food prep. The ergonomic and functional design provides you with 6 different grating/shredding/slicing options, making any other grater in your kitchen obsolete.<br/><br/>Grate vegetables like a pro, prepare both soft and hard kinds of cheese effortlessly, extract maximum flavor from citrus with a dedicated zester side, grate breadcrumbs or ginger using finer mesh, or slice cucumbers & other veggies in a breeze using the slicer plane. The Beille 6-in-1 kitchen gadget is a versatile tool that is both handy and indispensable.<br/><br/>Each side provides a different desired result:<br/>-Fine Shred (Zester): Ideal for shredding nutmeg, parmesan, garlic, citrus, fruit zests, and more <br/>-Slice: Make crisp slices from vegetables and medium-sized cheeses<br/>-Arc Slice - Ideal for chocolate, parmesan, and small vegetable ribbons for salad<br/>-Medium shred - Make crisp slices from cucumbers, tomatoes, and more<br/>-Coarse - Great for shredding firm vegetables, medium & hard cheese, ginger, and chocolate<br/>-Square shred - Great for shredding hard vegetables, bread and hard cheeses<br/><br/>Once you are done prepping all of your ingredients, the Beille hexagon stainless steel grater can easily be washed with soap and water or on the top rack of your dishwasher. It allows the food slicer to take up minimal storage space with a lightweight and compact design whether it is displayed on your counter or inside of a cabinet. Choose between two modern color options - seafoam green and coral pink. Our multi-sided food grater is a great gift idea for bridal showers, weddings, housewarmings, dinner party host gifts, or birthdays.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
